OHIO BAR ASSN.
v.
TIMBERWOLF LITIGATION & RESEARCH SERVS., L.L.C. 2019-0998 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 6, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On John Houk's motion to quash subpoena duces tecum. Relator, the Ohio State Bar Association, shall file a response, if any, to the motion within ten days.
